sed on enstrophy and overturn\nthresholds quantify the nature of turbulence between different regimes, while\nhighlighting the challenges of obtaining representative statistics in\nspatio-temporally intermittent flows. These insights may stimulate and assist\nthe development of numerical simulations with a higher degree of experimental\nrealism.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 16 Mar 2021 16:53:41 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-03-14"}
