V}}$). We additionally place constraints on the jet composition and magnetic\nfield strength in the innermost jet base region. Overall, this work\ndemonstrates that time-domain analysis is a powerful diagnostic tool for\nprobing jet physics, where we can accurately measure jet properties with\ntime-domain measurements alone.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 16 Mar 2021 20:48:58 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 24 Mar 2021 22:21:08 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-03-31"}
