d DCRNet also dramatically shortened the\nreconstruction time by nearly 10 thousand times for each scan, from around 80\nhours using conventional approaches to only 30 seconds.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 17 Mar 2021 00:26:51 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-07-20"}
