ic scaling and which can be directly related\nto $s_c / s_c^*$. Further, the Murnaghan EOS allows us to interpret $\\gamma$ as\na measure of intrinsic anharmonicity of intermolecular interactions that may be\ndirectly determined from the pressure derivative of the material bulk modulus.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 17 Mar 2021 03:11:51 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-03-18"}
