ual NLI and achieving state-of-the-art performance on common\nbenchmarks.\n  We make our code and dataset available at\nhttps://github.com/jahuerta92/siamese-inter-lingual-transformer.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 17 Mar 2021 13:23:53 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 18 Mar 2021 19:28:55 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Mon, 17 May 2021 08:22:07 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-05-18"}
